00:00:10.500 --> 00:00:13.180
and I'm a professor of
neurobiology and ophthalmology

00:00:13.180 --> 00:00:15.260
at Stanford School of Medicine.

00:00:15.260 --> 00:00:18.850
Today I have the pleasure of
introducing Dr. Anna Lembke.

00:00:18.850 --> 00:00:21.300
Dr. Lembke is a psychiatrist
and the chief of

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:23.650
the Addiction Medicine
Dual Diagnosis Clinic

00:00:23.650 --> 00:00:26.300
at Stanford University School of Medicine.

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:28.670
She's a psychiatrist who treats patients

00:00:28.670 --> 00:00:30.620
