00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:37.660
and behavioral addictions,

00:00:37.660 --> 00:00:40.040
such as gambling and sex addiction,

00:00:40.040 --> 00:00:42.410
as well as other types of addiction.

00:00:42.410 --> 00:00:43.760
