00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:46.590
I learned that there are
a huge range of behaviors

00:00:46.590 --> 00:00:50.020
and substances to which
people can become addicted to,

00:00:50.020 --> 00:00:52.960
and that there is a common
biological underpinning

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:54.780
of all those addictions.

00:00:54.780 --> 00:00:57.380
I also learned that there is a common path

00:00:57.380 --> 00:00:59.090
to the treatment and recovery

00:00:59.090 --> 00:01:01.230
from essentially all addictions.

00:01:01.230 --> 00:01:03.350
Dr. Lembke explained that to me

00:01:03.350 --> 00:01:06.640
and explained how to think
about and conceptualize

00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:08.050
our own addictions,

00:01:08.050 --> 00:01:10.130
as well as the addictions of other people

00:01:10.130 --> 00:01:13.300
who are struggling to get
treatment, move through treatment,

00:01:13.300 --> 00:01:15.360
