00:47:25.760 --> 00:47:27.160
That's a tricky one for me,

00:47:27.160 --> 00:47:29.573
because there are certain
things I just don't do well.

00:47:30.440 --> 00:47:32.040
But should we always be trying?

00:47:32.040 --> 00:47:36.260
I think that the tending to,
setting the horizon in closely

00:47:37.610 --> 00:47:39.680
and tending to things in
one's immediate environment,

00:47:39.680 --> 00:47:41.850
I think is very powerful and translates,

00:47:41.850 --> 00:47:42.860
- Yes.
- because again,

00:47:42.860 --> 00:47:45.700
I think the nervous system,
it performs algorithms.

00:47:45.700 --> 00:47:46.850
It has action steps.

00:47:46.850 --> 00:47:49.950
The brain doesn't evolve to do one thing,

00:47:49.950 --> 00:47:52.700
it evolves to be able
to use the same approach

00:47:52.700 --> 00:47:53.770
to doing lots of different things.

00:47:53.770 --> 00:47:55.210
- Yes.

