00:59:36.520 --> 00:59:39.250
important because I also had to

00:59:39.250 --> 00:59:42.330
come to an understanding of
this, and I feel that I have

00:59:42.330 --> 00:59:45.090
in my 20 years of seeing these patients.

00:59:45.090 --> 00:59:46.580
And of course addiction
is a spectrum disease,

00:59:46.580 --> 00:59:47.874
- Sure.
